mile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b02db679fa6e2584aa1bbde21f3a2243570c28","tid":516352,"uid":47340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T18:15:38.000Z","msg":"海邊踩真係好痴線<br />\n新竹後海邊段路大風到，逆風踩到屌曬鬼<br />\n不過依家冬天風向應該唔同？"},{"pid":"0ca8798c925ac89c5690fd4c01971fe54282c8da","tid":516352,"uid":21740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1月中去台中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打去台中旅行定踩單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去旅行咋<br />\n廢丁踩單車只識踩直線⋯"},{"pid":"eb70de0f5453155d92545ebfa8cce454101168ef","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"3/1 今日0800係旅館食早餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/005427_4901c3a3b98c5ffc6802c3b8cb2cd544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F005427_4901c3a3b98c5ffc6802c3b8cb2cd544.jpg&h=6a8af646&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0681a3d2f4fe47417434c1835459e8c115f69cc6","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"手殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  禁快左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/005536_8a812e65e78427e2d1b08b1a50b25bfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F005536_8a812e65e78427e2d1b08b1a50b25bfe.jpg&h=df2f9a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n種類都係粥粉麵飯...<br />\n好唔好食見人見智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要係食飽上路<br />\n<br />\n0900 點係新竹火車站出發<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/005721_72eb1d223837193c905b08332e0a79d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F005721_72eb1d223837193c905b08332e0a79d1.jpg&h=7719601d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踩左一陣就到台61...風情海岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/005813_1bafab86443a157f582723c0316795ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F005813_1bafab86443a157f582723c0316795ec.jpg&h=bd4817f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後沿61線行...挑戰後龍坡前的補給站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/005949_89b644b08cc582b5fd9fc63d7af5000c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F005949_89b644b08cc582b5fd9fc63d7af5000c.jpg&h=6e386720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後龍坡？塔利班單車兄弟係未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後單車哥死左，單車弟成功到達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落後龍坡都接近一點<br />\n食返間七仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/010257_600395668fec6d0e825add036e3a65e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F010257_600395668fec6d0e825add036e3a65e7.jpg&h=bd76c92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後踩去台中既高美濕地<br />\n路程中，單車兄再次身亡，一度令旅程膠著<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/010409_0b112ce13265159604477942e2ba45db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F010409_0b112ce13265159604477942e2ba45db.jpg&h=25c2a8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係最後大家抽晒筋之下都成功到達高美濕地<br />\n好靚既一個地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/010508_60b5d5a7357e729e5e9c65ed0ee3edb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F010508_60b5d5a7357e729e5e9c65ed0ee3edb9.jpg&h=b466b848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後送上單車兄弟既一張鐵達尼<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/010619_531764096be041b24509076d57aafd6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F010619_531764096be041b24509076d57aafd6b.jpg&h=09f73479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明天會休息一天，後日會去嘉義<br />\n究竟單車哥可唔可以一洗頹氣<br />\n大家拭目以待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c47a13c5b6738cf3da173d443e89dfb41f13992","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"今日食左既牛肉麵同咖哩飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/203328_28fde232b7d212767856a2cfca69d732.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F203328_28fde232b7d212767856a2cfca69d732.jpg&h=b56d3037&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6865c4c0f154d37263fe4cd9c771bc0980a5f3ac","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1月中去台中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打去台中旅行定踩單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去旅行咋<br />\n廢丁踩單車只識踩直線⋯</blockquote><br />\n幾多個人黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f154a6075ca16bdf2c4f4a6bb784c768540d743","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海邊踩真係好痴線<br />\n新竹後海邊段路大風到，逆風踩到屌曬鬼<br />\n不過依家冬天風向應該唔同？</blockquote><br />\n暫時都無遇到逆風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78818fcc3a3d66512e550e84b99d9ea0ae0b5670","tid":516352,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"鳥哥到租車?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打玩1個月? <br />\n去唔去台灣四點?"},{"pid":"c409d8db077b88c472f7358c1d46adcf95abf4e7","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳥哥到租車?[img]assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif[/img] <br />\n<br />\n巴打玩1個月? <br />\n去唔去台灣四點?</blockquote><br />\n係啊 玩一個月左右<br />\n去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de20314090d2e496d640c278715195fa40098126","tid":516352,"uid":80696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de22d6ba7796e4a330362cdc04fc2a30a4c5023","tid":516352,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"裝一個 apps 叫導航王 <br />\n可以免費 30天 <br />\n<br />\n有齊飯店/7仔/好玩  <br />\n<br />\n我係絕望果陣<br />\n台灣人介紹我用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdcee6d27348b60e133a21232cfc9a66ca35a32","tid":516352,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:11:20.000Z","msg":"1個月可以超慢踩 <br />\n<br />\n用最hea踩<br />\n時速 10~15k<br />\n<br />\n每日 60~70k 就可以<br />\n<br />\n仲可以大把時間剩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c161568575ea0738c560be57a463fd8cbba7ea1","tid":516352,"uid":21740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1月中去台中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打去台中旅行定踩單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去旅行咋<br />\n廢丁踩單車只識踩直線⋯</blockquote><br />\n幾多個人黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n獨遊咋"},{"pid":"08e3a8cbdd5e17dae3c0ea282457e367d3e76a87","tid":516352,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"睇post G持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d033a15c0b0996435fd7b8c5d6cceaa99d5a23","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"琴日休息食左個咖哩飯之後<br />\n我地行左陣就去左食下午茶...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/092404_db5110e70d6f3413b29d99adb98bd156.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F092404_db5110e70d6f3413b29d99adb98bd156.jpg&h=386b242f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台式拉麵+紅茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅茶唔錯，拉麵試一次就夠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩樣加埋岩岩好100NT<br />\n<br />\n夜晚行行下逢甲夜市<br />\n單車兄見到玩槍既檔攤 諗返起以前係cso槍林彈雨既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/092514_e0ee2e11e0437336992ee140d2820c68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F092514_e0ee2e11e0437336992ee140d2820c68.jpg&h=60eb1a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n單車兄憑住一支AK47 開拓佢既夢想<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/092727_eb96ba89bce06f223cf8e04a7593b4da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F092727_eb96ba89bce06f223cf8e04a7593b4da.jpg&h=55701802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頹廢既一日分享完<br />\n今日0930開始出發去嘉義<br />\n天陰陰 下起一陣雨粉<br />\n單車兄有份執著<br />\n為左安全 佢單飛去左截的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/092955_98c8bd97f1a17de201d13ccdd1e8d179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F092955_98c8bd97f1a17de201d13ccdd1e8d179.jpg&h=4d4da851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後既90公里<br />\n我會緊貼單車弟黎出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台中》嘉義<br />\n出發！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ee1f5af10c7d60cbdf6cc303de2861bb067497","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇post G持 [img]assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a592554785fafcdc44a4f26c13f3ddf23b8278","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1月中去台中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打去台中旅行定踩單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去旅行咋<br />\n廢丁踩單車只識踩直線⋯</blockquote><br />\n幾多個人黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n獨遊咋</blockquote><br />\n黎台中玩幾多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375df95b949ef4624d4e4c61c6c65a61628ad260","tid":516352,"uid":5773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:33:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1個月可以超慢踩 <br />\n<br />\n用最hea踩<br />\n時速 10~15k<br />\n<br />\n每日 60~70k 就可以<br />\n<br />\n仲可以大把時間剩 [img]assets/faces/xm/devil.png[/img]</blockquote><br />\n好啊巴打<br />\n多謝你既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對於新手既我地覺得好實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時間再交流一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2ce8ca96384138be2c10292757425c18a7fd44","tid":516352,"uid":